  "text": "Analyses were performed on a modified intent-to-treat principle, excluding only diagnostic errors and withdrawals of consent. Censored endpoints were estimated by the nonparametric KaplanMeier method [CITATION_1] and then compared between randomized groups by the log-rank test. In estimating relapses, we took into account competing risks, i.e., deaths in first complete remission, using cumulative incidence curves and then compared results using the Gray test, whereas a cause-specific Cox model was used to estimate cause-specific hazard ratios.",
